{"tid":562649,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[實驗] 連續30日 - 每日冥想 , 每日運動 (帶氧)","createTime":"2018-02-16T06:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T17:25:50.000Z","uid":123335,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce6de4f35048d293865c390b4a46c3459a2ba8a","tid":562649,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T06:31:43.000Z","msg":"上個 Post 既經驗所得 , <br />\n每日運動 (帶氧) 既好處非常之明顯 <br />\n包括提升精神 , 清醒度, 理性邏輯, 心情, 情緒, 睡眠質素 , 意志力 <br />\n所以將會繼續多30日 <br />\n計劃每日運動 (帶氧) : 最少30mins ; 最多 45mins <br />\n運動方式會以慢跑為主 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\b最近我打算試埋冥想 (mindfulness meditation) <br />\n每日共30分鐘, 每次至少 10 分鐘 <br />\n據聞冥想會對大腦既皮質 灰質 杏仁核等結構有臨床上既變化 <br />\n會提升專注力，提升創意，提升記憶力，減低壓力及焦慮 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一如以往, <br />\n樓主會一路做記錄 , 觀察自己既變化 <br />\n同埋會每日上黎報告  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大年初一<br />\nDay 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3594d313db08a0bd218ef06179cc8e4d0ab552","tid":562649,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"岩岩冥想左 20 mins <br />\n大腦係明顯有休息, 放鬆既感覺 , 但唔太強烈 <br />\n睇黎要日日keep 住做一排先有明顯變化 <br />\n<br />\n然後岩岩跑左15mins <br />\n成個人醒晒 , 再一次進入覺醒狀態, 腦轉數極快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5260d382529c7d06231f17f25adaadcebdb15521","tid":562649,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T13:27:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35d79116f1c11923267f3899aa788512bbe6b8fa","tid":562649,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"822b3fcf7fa2b7197a4c7ea2692f11f64e379fc1","tid":562649,"uid":7306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"樓主有無tg<br />\n有d嘢想同你討論"},{"pid":"a8dd357a05310393244c2ea4da9968c1e2764989","tid":562649,"uid":128616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"